{"type": "article", "id": 25649, "title": "带LED照明系统的瑜伽垫", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-19T07:13:01Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 45, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702170323GhyfxmLcnSpKX8iI.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是一款智能健身垫，使用了来自丹麦 Kvadrat 的羊毛面料。它可以连接上 TERA app 来检测施加的压力变化，以监督动作的标准。此外，垫子上均匀分布着小的三角纹路是一个 LED 照明系统。它可以引导当身体与垫子接触的动作。<a href=\"http://tera.lunar-europe.com/Solution.html\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170321htrLMEVPlOekA0cB.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170321JAzqDKhTynSc0G9g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170322ps8yqU9rOucVRXwg.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021703227TSCuHJ85UPlhtcR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170323qMmuTenjYGchV271.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}